    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 9. Habitus views of Agrilus spp.; scale bars = 1 mm: 1 – 2., holotype, A. rifkindi, dorsal and lateral views; 3., holotype, A. rifkindi pueblae, dorsal view; 4 – 5., holotype, A. obrienorum, dorsal and lateral views; 6 – 7., holotype, A. giesberti, dorsal and lateral views; 8 – 9., holotype, A. anthaxioides, dorsal and lateral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274806/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274808>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18 – 25. Male genitalia of Agrilus spp.; scale bars = 1 mm: 18., holotype, A. rifkindi; 19., holotype, A. obrienorum; 20., holotype, A. giesberti; 21., holotype, A. anthaxioides; 22., holotype, A. leucaenae; 23., holotype, A. chrysobothroides; 24., holotype, A. paramacer; 25., holotype, A. parkinsoniae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

